iches Zeugnis der kulturellen und politischen Entwicklung in der DDR zwischen dem Mauerbau im August 1961 und dem kulturpolitischen Kahlschlag von Ende 1965.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a FA license: uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/free-access-policy uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aGerman literaturey20th centuryxHistory and criticismvCongresses. 0aGerman literaturezGermany (East)xHistory and criticismvCongresses. 0aGerman literaturezGermany (West)xHistory and criticismvCongresses. 0aGerman literature. 4aDDR. 4aKulturpolitik. 4aLiteratur. 4aOstblockländer. 4aSchriftstellerverband der DDR. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh1 aScherstjanoi, Elke, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978348658560540uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/9783486702798zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486702798zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783486702798.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-GPHc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OGSc2005d2012